Babylonia - Commercial District A

War not only brings ruins and devastation, but also carves wounds in the hearts of those who experience it—wounds that are difficult to heal... Commissioned by Ross, the Gray Raven Commandant decides to help a soldier suffering from psychological trauma to emerge from the shadows of the past.
